name: Dalton Bednar
text: Ten stars easily. This is a volunteer group where anyone of any financial or educational level can get together to enhance our skills. Please at least visit, it'll let you know what's possible with hope, work, dedication, learning, and collaboration.

resp.text: Thank you Dalton for the stellar review! we're glad you found what you were looking for here at RMM!

name: Carlo Rezzonico
text:
RMM is the place I've been dreaming about finding! Labs for woodworking, metal working, electronics, fibers, pottery, biology and other crafts! I would spend all day there if I had time.

If you have an idea, you can count on the space to have the right tools to get the job done and the right people to help you along the way (and even better, if no one knows how to do something, there will be somebody that is excited to learn with you!).

name: Adam Smith
text: If you're interested in making stuff but don't have a space or tools of your own this is a great place to be. The people are great.

name: H. Fox
text: Really neat place 3d printers, metal working, woodworking, circuits designing and repair, a ceramics kiln and lots of classes on meet up.

name: John Woods
text: Nerd Central, serious about inventing things that solve life's dilemmas.
